orage'错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice无法连接到Redis存储后端，导致购物车功能完全失效\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2出现158次'Error status code FailedPrecondition with detail Can't access cart storage'错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务依赖cartservice，因cartservice故障而无法处理购物车请求\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多个frontend实例报告'failed to add to cart: rpc error: code = FailedPrecondition desc = Can't access cart storage'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现：**\n\n1. **主要故障模式**：Redis存储服务连接问题\n   - cartservice无法连接到redis-cart:6379\n   - 这导致购物车存储功能完全失效\n\n2. **影响范围**：\n   - 所有frontend实例都受到影响（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）\n   - 所有cartservice实例都报告存储访问错误\n\n3. **故障类型**：端口连接问题\n   - 检测到`port`和`connection refused`关键词\n   - 可能是Redis服务端口6379无法访问或配置错误\n\n建议立即检查redis-cart服务的状态和网络连接配置。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对故障期间指标数据的全面分析，我发现了多个显著的异常模式。以下是初始扫描阶段的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio和error_ratio出现显著异常，p99值从0.0飙升至51.82，表明该Pod在处理请求时出现严重错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio和error_ratio的p99值从0.0上升到51.82，变化率2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio和error_ratio异常，p99值从0.0上升到23.4，同时pod_cpu_usage出现1.6593倍的增长\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio p99值23.4，pod_cpu_usage从0.01增长到0.11\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个frontend实例的error_ratio、server_error_ratio和rrt_max指标异常，表明前端服务整体性能下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0 error_ratio从0.0到0.66，frontend-1 server_error_ratio从0.0到0.64，rrt_max普遍增长1.5-1.6倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt和rrt_max指标严重异常，rrt_max从175415.0增长到95951.0，p99值从22